  <brief_title>MESNA for Prevention of Acute Deterioration of Renal Function Following Contrast Agent Application</brief_title>
  <official_title>MESNA Zur Prophylaxe Der Kontrastmittel-Induzierten Nephropathie</official_title>
  <sponsors>
